thread.title: Dollar Rises Ahead of Fed Meeting

author: Ira Iosebashvili
title: Dollar Rises Ahead of Fed Meeting
text:
The dollar rose Monday, as investors locked in profits on bets against the U.S. currency ahead of a Federal Reserve meeting later this week.
The Wall Street Journal Dollar Index, which measures the U.S. currency against a basket of 16 others, was recently up 0.4% to 83.38.
